      "*": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><p>\n<aside role=\"region\" class=\"portable-infobox pi-background pi-border-color pi-theme-Chapter pi-layout-default\">\n<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-item-spacing pi-title pi-secondary-background\" data-source=\"title\">To Live</h2>\n\n<figure class=\"pi-item pi-image\" data-source=\"image\">\n\t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/4/40/Chapter_79.png/revision/latest?cb=20130121040155\" class=\"image image-thumbnail\" title=\"Chapter 79\">\n\t\t<img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/4/40/Chapter_79.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/268?cb=20130121040155\" srcset=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/4/40/Chapter_79.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/268?cb=20130121040155 1x, https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/4/40/Chapter_79.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/536?cb=20130121040155 2x\" class=\"pi-image-thumbnail\" data-relevant=\"1\" alt=\"Chapter 79\" width=\"270\" height=\"194\" data-image-key=\"Chapter_79.png\" data-image-name=\"Chapter 79.png\" />\n\t\t\n\t</a>\n\t\n</figure>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Chapter Info</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"vol\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Volume:</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Volume_9\" title=\"Volume 9\">9</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"chapter\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Chapter:</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">79</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"jname\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Japanese Title:</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">生きる</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"rname\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Romanized Title:</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><i>Ikiru</i></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"ename\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Viz Title:</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">To Live</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"page\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Pages:</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">19</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"date2\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Release Date:</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">March 8, 1999<span class=\"plainlinks\" title=\"Release dates obtained from http&#58;//www.thegrandline.com\"><sup><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.thegrandline.com/odatocLIVE.htm\">[ref]</a></sup></span></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"jump\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">WSJ Issue:</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">1999 Issue 15</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"anime\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Anime:</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/One_Piece:_The_Movie\" title=\"One Piece: The Movie\">One Piece: The Movie</a> (p. 2-3)<br /><a href=\"/wiki/Episode_36\" title=\"Episode 36\">Episode 36</a> (p. 1, 4-19)<br /></div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<table class=\"pi-horizontal-group pi-horizontal-group-no-labels\">\n\t<caption class=\"pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-secondary-background pi-item-spacing\">Chapter Chronology</caption>\n\t\n\t<tbody>\n\t<tr>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\">← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_78\" title=\"Chapter 78\">Previous</a></td>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_80\" title=\"Chapter 80\">Next</a> →</td>\n\t\n\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n</section>\n</aside>\n\n<b>Chapter 79</b> is titled \"To Live\".\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Cover_Page\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Cover Page</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Short_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Short Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Long_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Long Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quick_Reference\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quick Reference</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Chapter_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chapter Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Characters\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Author_Comment\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Author Comment</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Trivia\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Trivia</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Site_Navigation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Site Navigation</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Cover_Page\">Cover Page</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_79%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Cover_Page#Color_Spread\" title=\"Cover Page\">Color Spread</a>: The <a href=\"/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates\" title=\"Straw Hat Pirates\">Straw Hat Pirates</a> in a Wild West frontier town. <a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Zoro</a>&#160;is riding a huge black panther; <a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a>&#160;is lounging against a second, heavily drunk panther; <a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a>&#160;is pointing a pistol straight ahead; and <a href=\"/wiki/Sanji\" title=\"Sanji\">Sanji</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a> are returning from a supply run, arms laden with bags and barrels.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Short_Summary\">Short Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_79%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After being kidnapped, <a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a> became a member of <a href=\"/wiki/Arlong\" title=\"Arlong\">Arlong</a>'s crew.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Long_Summary\">Long Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_79%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After <a href=\"/wiki/Bell-m%C3%A8re\" title=\"Bell-mère\">Bell-mère</a>'s death, <a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a> was kidnapped when Arlong discovered her ability for drawing maps. All the villagers decided to fight to take her back, but she suddenly came back by herself, revealing that she was now part of Arlong's crew. She even showed that&#160;she could&#160;earn all the money she wanted. Disgusted by this selfish behavior, the villagers rejected her. But when <a href=\"/wiki/Nojiko\" title=\"Nojiko\">Nojiko</a> went to her mother's grave, Nami was already sitting there. She explained to her sister that in order to accomplish their mother's last wish and live, they could not rebel against <a href=\"/wiki/Arlong\" title=\"Arlong\">Arlong</a> who was too strong for them. Instead she decided to draw maps for him, revealing that she would be able to buy her village back for <span style=\"white-space:nowrap;\"><span class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Belly\" title=\"Belly\"><img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/d/de/Beli.png/revision/latest?cb=20141206091723\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"12\" height=\"20\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Beli.png\" data-image-key=\"Beli.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" /></a></span></span>100,000,000.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quick_Reference\">Quick Reference</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_79%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D4&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chapter_Notes\">Chapter Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_79%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D5&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a>'s flashback continues.\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Arlong\" title=\"Arlong\">Arlong</a> kidnaps Nami after discovering her cartography talents.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Genzo\" title=\"Genzo\">Genzo</a>'s scars come from a fight against <a href=\"/wiki/Kuroobi\" title=\"Kuroobi\">Kuroobi</a>.</li>\n<li>Nami joins the <a href=\"/wiki/Arlong_Pirates\" title=\"Arlong Pirates\">Arlong Pirates</a>.</li>\n<li>Arlong decides to release his hold on the village if Nami gives him <span style=\"white-space:nowrap;\"><span class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Belly\" title=\"Belly\"><img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/d/de/Beli.png/revision/latest?cb=20141206091723\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"12\" height=\"20\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Beli.png\" data-image-key=\"Beli.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" /></a></span></span>100,000,000.</li></ul></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters\">Characters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_79%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D6&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table class=\"CharTable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/Pirate\" title=\"Pirate\">Pirates</a>\n</th>\n<th>Citizens\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates\" title=\"Straw Hat Pirates\">Straw Hat Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Monkey D. Luffy</a> <i>(cover)</i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Roronoa Zoro</a> <i>(cover)</i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a> <i>(cover)</i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Sanji\" title=\"Sanji\">Sanji</a> <i>(cover)</i></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Arlong_Pirates\" title=\"Arlong Pirates\">Arlong Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Arlong\" title=\"Arlong\">Arlong</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Hatchan\" title=\"Hatchan\">Hatchan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Chew\" title=\"Chew\">Chew</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Kuroobi\" title=\"Kuroobi\">Kuroobi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Pisaro\" title=\"Pisaro\">Pisaro</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Cocoyasi_Village\" title=\"Cocoyasi Village\">Cocoyasi Village</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Nojiko\" title=\"Nojiko\">Nojiko</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Genzo\" title=\"Genzo\">Genzo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Bell-m%C3%A8re\" title=\"Bell-mère\">Bell-mère</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Nako\" title=\"Nako\">Nako</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Mummy_Mee\" title=\"Mummy Mee\">Mummy Mee</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Daddy_Dee\" title=\"Daddy Dee\">Daddy Dee</a></li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Author_Comment\">Author Comment</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_79%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D7&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><br />\n</p><table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin: auto; text-align: center; width:50%\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">Author Comment</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:90%\"><div class=\"tabber wds-tabber\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper with-bottom-border\"><ul class=\"wds-tabs\"><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\" data-hash=\"Translation\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Translation</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Original\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Original</a></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\"><p><br />\nWas shocked by the new <i>Gundam</i>. <i>Turn A Gundam</i>. As someone who has been a fan of the first <i>Gundam</i> series since elementary school I never thought it would evolve into…that! So it's come to this!!</p></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content\"><p><br />\n新しいガンダムにビビった。ターンAガンダム。小学生の時にハマってたファーストガンダムからまさかああ進化するとは…！ああきたか!!</p></div></div>—<a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\">Eiichiro Oda</a></td><td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\"><img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/a/ad/Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20230801133230\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Eiichiro Oda WSJ Avatar.png\" data-image-key=\"Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"><i>English translation by <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.thegrandline.com/odatocLIVE.htm\">Greg Werner</a>. For comprehensive translation credits, see <a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments#Translation_Credits\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">here</a>.</i></td></tr>\n\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\">Trivia</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_79%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D8&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>In the chapter's initial publishing in <a href=\"/wiki/Shonen_Jump\" title=\"Shonen Jump\"><i>Weekly Shonen Jump</i></a>, the first two story pages were printed in full color.</li>\n<li>This chapter's cover page was—redrawn to remove <a href=\"/wiki/Sanji\" title=\"Sanji\">Sanji</a> and include <a href=\"/wiki/Gill_Bastar\" title=\"Gill Bastar\">Gill Bastar</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Wild_Joe\" title=\"Wild Joe\">Wild Joe</a>—featured in the credits montage of <i><a href=\"/wiki/One_Piece:_The_Movie\" title=\"One Piece: The Movie\">One Piece: The Movie</a></i>.</li>\n<li>This is the second cover wherein Nami appears as one of the <a href=\"/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates\" title=\"Straw Hat Pirates\">Straw Hats</a> while she is actually still with the Arlong Pirates.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Site_Navigation\">Site Navigation</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_79%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D9&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"toccolours\" style=\"margin:auto; text-align:center; width:80%;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left;\">\n<p><b>← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_78\" title=\"Chapter 78\">Previous Chapter</a></b>\n<